</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>UPDATE_DIRECTION</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>이 단계는 실제로 <computeroutput>ControllerImplModelUpdater::Update()</computeroutput>와 <computeroutput>Controller::Relayouter::*</computeroutput>에서 사용된다.</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md__2home_2runner_2work_2dali-ui-documentation_2dali-ui-documentation_2dali-doc-gen_2repos_2dali717c9451db5cc9e2541c83af4d78ce1f_1autotoc_md30">
<title>단계별 의미</title>
<sect3 id="md__2home_2runner_2work_2dali-ui-documentation_2dali-ui-documentation_2dali-doc-gen_2repos_2dali717c9451db5cc9e2541c83af4d78ce1f_1autotoc_md31">
